Three armed suspects, who robbed a man of his bag after he exited the bank in Fordsburg, Johannesburg, opened fire on police before fleeing the scene in a white BMW. The incident happened on Wednesday afternoon. Video footage of the incident circulated on social media. It is alleged that the victim was accosted by three armed men after leaving the bank. They demanded the bag he was carrying. When the victim ran to a nearby store, he was followed and robbed at gunpoint. Masondo said the robbers opened fire on police officers who attended to the robbery.No officer was injured, Masondo said. This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. 2019 BMW R 1250 GS Review We spend some time with the new BMW R 1250 GS to see what exactly has changed and what makes it such a popular adventure bike around the world.